1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:02,108
"MOSFILM" production

2
00:00:16,878 --> 00:00:19,548
What is your name?

3
00:00:24,221 --> 00:00:27,559
My name is Yuri Zhary.

4
00:00:35,569 --> 00:00:38,240
Where are you from?

5
00:00:51,590 --> 00:00:54,010
I'm from Kharkov.

6
00:00:56,262 --> 00:00:58,181
What school do you go to?

7
00:01:01,270 --> 00:01:04,441
I go to a trade school.

8
00:01:09,614 --> 00:01:12,951
We'll begin now.

9
00:01:14,037 --> 00:01:16,290
Look at me closely.

10
00:01:19,334 --> 00:01:21,629
Look right into my eyes.

11
00:01:44,325 --> 00:01:47,288
Concentrate on my hand.

12
00:01:47,956 --> 00:01:50,501
My hand is drawing you back.

13
00:02:13,031 --> 00:02:15,033
Concentrate!

14
00:02:17,703 --> 00:02:19,706
Your attention
is on your hands.

15
00:02:23,419 --> 00:02:26,088
Your hands are becoming tense!

16
00:02:27,717 --> 00:02:31,054
You're concentrating your
will, your great desire

17
00:02:31,430 --> 00:02:33,724
to succeed on your hands.

18
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:38,396
Your hands are becoming
very tense.

19
00:02:44,781 --> 00:02:48,786
Look at your fingers.
They're becoming tense.

20
00:02:50,413 --> 00:02:54,418
The tension from here will
flow to your fingers.

21
00:03:02,137 --> 00:03:05,682
When I say "3", your hands
will become rigid.

22
00:03:08,437 --> 00:03:11,106
One, two,

23
00:03:12,192 --> 00:03:14,694
three! Your hands are rigid.

24
00:03:15,111 --> 00:03:17,115
You can not move your hands.

25
00:03:17,782 --> 00:03:21,788
You try to move them,
but can not.

26
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:28,463
I'll relieve the tension now,

27
00:03:29,131 --> 00:03:33,135
and you will speak clearly
and effortlessly.

28
00:03:36,848 --> 00:03:41,521
And you will speak loudly and
clearly all your life.

29
00:03:48,489 --> 00:03:52,495
I'll remove the tension from
your hands and speech.

30
00:03:55,164 --> 00:03:57,834
One, two,

31
00:03:58,502 --> 00:03:59,838
three!

32
00:04:01,173 --> 00:04:05,427
- Say "I can speak".
- I can speak.

33
